title: Cannot download League of Legends
body:
It load to 33% and an error message pops up.

It says
> Unspecified error please check the logs

replies.body: Once the patcher hits 33% is when you actually start downloading all of the new patch files. An unspecified error at this point means something is probably blocking your network from the patching servers, meaning it can't grab any of the data and the patcher doesn't know why. Check out the steps in our [**connection faq**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) and let me know if you're still having problems getting that patch!
